Modifications from upstream cytostack/openwolf @ bd69835:

  2026-04-08  Add Dart language support. (commit f68be48)

  2026-04-11  Bind dashboard HTTP/WS server to 127.0.0.1 by default; reject
              cross-origin WebSocket upgrades. Closes a security exposure
              where the dashboard's POST /api/cron/run endpoint (which
              executes `claude -p`) was reachable from the LAN.
              (commit 6afcf94)

  2026-04-11  Extend scanner CODE_EXTENSIONS and token estimator CODE_EXTS
              to cover Kotlin, Swift, Objective-C, C++ variants, C#, Ruby,
              PHP, Lua, Vue, Svelte, HTML, Protobuf, GraphQL, Terraform,
              and shell variants. (commit d71d925)

  2026-04-19  Incorporate upstream PR #18 by @jasper-trustworks: git
              worktree support. Shared brain files (cerebrum, buglog,
              token-ledger, identity, config, OPENWOLF.md) live in the
              main repo's .wolf/ when running inside a worktree;
              session-specific files (anatomy, memory) stay per-worktree.
              Originally proposed at cytostack/openwolf#18, closed
              unmerged by upstream maintainer.

